videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland buries a 3-pointer and stares down the Houston student section.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cumberland stares down Houston crowd after 3) 2020/03/01

videos.headline: Cumberland stares down Houston crowd after 3

videos.description: Houston's Caleb Mills drives to the rim and banks in a difficult lefty shot over two Cincinnati defenders while drawing the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mills hits tough and-1 over 2 defenders) 2020/03/01

videos.headline: Mills hits tough and-1 over 2 defenders

videos.description: Caleb Mills buries a 3-pointer for Houston and leaves his shooting hand up for everyone in the Cougars crowd to see.
videos.headline: Mills drains 3, leaves it hanging

videos.description: Cincinnati head coach John Brannen has to be restrained by his players and assistant coaches after receiving a technical foul.

videos.description: Houston's DeJon Jarreau flies in for a massive poster slam on Mamoudou Diarra, but gets rejected by the rim.
videos.headline: Jarreau blows big time dunk
